Package de.unisb.cs.st.javaslicer.variables

Interface Variable

All Known Implementing Classes:
ArrayElement, LocalVariable, ObjectField, StackEntry, StaticField
public interface Variable
A variable is a place where information can be stored during dynamic slicing. This is either a local variable, an object field (static or not), an array element or an element of the operand stack.
Author:
Clemens Hammacher
